snippet.description:

[Subscribe: https://bit.ly/C4_News_Subscribe]

They are trying to agree on a more demonstrable commitment to peacekeeping in Ukraine and get President Zelenskyy's relationship with President Trump back on track after Friday's bust-up in the White House.

UK Prime Minister Keir Starmer spoke before the talks of assembling a coalition of the willing to add to Britain and France's commitment to troops on the ground to deter Russia from invading again.

#LetsGameItOut #OperaGX #simulation

----------

Check it out on Steam ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/305620/The_Long_Dark/

More about The Long Dark (from Steam):

Bright lights flare across the night sky. The wind rages outside the thin walls of your wooden cabin. A wolf howls in the distance. You look at the meager supplies in your pack, and wish for the days before the power mysteriously went out. How much longer will you survive?

Welcome to THE LONG DARK, the innovative exploration-survival experience Wired magazine calls "the pinnacle of an entire genre".

THE LONG DARK is a thoughtful, exploration-survival experience that challenges solo players to think for themselves as they explore an expansive frozen wilderness in the aftermath of a geomagnetic disaster. There are no zombies -- only you, the cold, and all the threats Mother Nature can muster.

THE LONG DARK: SURVIVAL EDITION brings you the genre-defining Survival Mode, honed after years of open development and frequent updates. Widely considered the paramount Survival game of all time, SURVIVAL EDITION gives you pure focus on THE LONG DARK’s Survival Sandbox -- the experience that started it all!

In THE LONG DARK, you are getting both the genre-defining Survival Mode, honed after years of open development and frequent updates, and the award-winning episodic narrative mode, WINTERMUTE.

Included with both THE LONG DARK: SURVIVAL EDITION and THE LONG DARK, Survival Mode is the free-form, non-narrative Survival Sandbox that has defined the genre since launching on Steam in 2014. After years of open development and dozens of major updates, THE LONG DARK now stands at the pinnacle of the entire genre. Survival is your only goal, and death your only end. Make your own survival story with every game.

The game that defined death for the survival genre. When you die in Survival, your save is deleted. Every decision matters.

The game challenges players to think for themselves by providing the information but never the answers. You have to earn the right to survive.

Monitor your Hunger, Thirst, Fatigue, and Cold as you struggle to balance resources with the energy needed to obtain them. Every action costs Calories, and time is your most precious resource. Choose your path carefully.

Over 100 gear items including Tools, Light Sources, Weapons, First Aid supplies, Clothing, and more.

Explore a 50+ square kilometer Northern Canadian wilderness spanning 12 major regions and all the zones that connect them in search of life-saving supplies. Distant mountains, coastal towns, mines, farmlands, and a huge expanse of brutal winter wilderness to test your survival mettle.

Hunt, fish, trap, climb, map, search for life-saving food and gear items, and try to avoid dying from the hostile wildlife, succumbing to hypothermia, frostbite, or dysentery (amongst other uncomfortable afflictions), find and maintain your life-saving gear. Hunt and be hunted by: Wolves, Bears, Moose, Rabbits, Deers, Crows, and more to come in future updates.

Four distinct Experience Modes let you find a challenge level you are comfortable with, such as Pilgrim Mode, which is meant to be quiet and pensive, all the way to Interloper Mode, where only the most experienced survivors have a chance to last a week. If none of the four Experiences suits you, use Custom Mode settings to tailor your Survival Mode game to your specific tastes.

Features the music of Sascha Dikiciyan.

Several standalone Challenge Modes offer objective-based experiences designed to last 1-3 hours each.

snippet.title: I Bought an Abandoned House on a Remote Island - Surviving Winter
snippet.description:
Winter has taken over the island, and living off-grid out here is no joke. With no roads, no power, and the North Atlantic cutting us off from the mainland, every day is a new challenge.

In this video, we take you deep into remote winter living here in outport Newfoundland. Showing the challenges of staying warm, hauling water, and keeping boats from freezing in subzero temperatures. We rely on an old stone well for drinking water, cut firewood to heat the abandoned house, and battle ice, wind, and isolation just to get through the season.

Winter on an off-grid island means nothing comes easy—everything freezes, things break, and survival is a daily grind. Later in the video, we finally get off the island and head to the mainland for a much-needed break, snowmobiling through Newfoundland’s backcountry with friends.

This is what off-grid island living looks like in winter—cold, unpredictable, but one heck of an adventure.

pt-BR.title: Comprei uma casa abandonada em uma ilha remota - Sobrevivendo ao inverno
pt-BR.description:
O inverno tomou conta da ilha, e viver fora da rede aqui não é brincadeira. Sem estradas, sem energia e o Atlântico Norte nos isolando do continente, cada dia é um novo desafio.

Neste vídeo, levamos você para o remoto inverno vivendo aqui no outport Newfoundland. Mostrando os desafios de se manter aquecido, transportar água e evitar que os barcos congelem em temperaturas abaixo de zero. Dependemos de um velho poço de pedra para beber água, cortamos lenha para aquecer a casa abandonada e lutamos contra o gelo, o vento e o isolamento apenas para passar a estação.

O inverno em uma ilha fora da rede significa que nada é fácil — tudo congela, as coisas quebram e a sobrevivência é uma rotina diária. Mais tarde no vídeo, finalmente saímos da ilha e seguimos para o continente para uma pausa muito necessária, andando de snowmobile pelo interior de Newfoundland com amigos.

É assim que a vida em uma ilha fora da rede parece no inverno — fria, imprevisível, mas uma aventura e tanto.

ja.title: 離島の廃屋を買った - 冬を乗り切る
ja.description:
島は冬に覆われ、オフグリッド生活は冗談ではありません。道路も電気もなく、北大西洋が本土から私たちを切り離しているため、毎日が新たな挑戦です。

この動画では、ニューファンドランド島の沖合の辺鄙な冬の生活の奥深くにご案内します。暖かく過ごし、水を運び、氷点下の気温で船が凍らないようにする難しさを紹介しています。飲み水は古い石の井戸に頼り、廃屋を暖めるために薪を切り、この季節を乗り切るために氷、風、孤立と戦っています。

オフグリッド島の冬は、何も簡単にはいきません。すべてが凍り、物が壊れ、生き延びることが毎日の苦労です。動画の後半では、ようやく島を出て本土に向かい、友人たちとニューファンドランド島の奥地をスノーモービルで走り、待望の休暇を取ります。

これが、オフグリッド島の冬の生活です。寒くて予測できませんが、とんでもない冒険です。

it.title: Ho comprato una casa abbandonata su un'isola remota - Sopravvivere all'inverno
it.description:
L'inverno ha preso il sopravvento sull'isola e vivere fuori dalla rete elettrica qui non è uno scherzo. Senza strade, senza elettricità e con l'Atlantico settentrionale che ci separa dalla terraferma, ogni giorno è una nuova sfida.

In questo video, ti portiamo nel profondo della vita invernale remota qui nel porto di Terranova. Mostrando le sfide di stare al caldo, trasportare acqua ed evitare che le barche si congelino a temperature sotto lo zero. Facciamo affidamento su un vecchio pozzo di pietra per bere acqua, tagliamo legna da ardere per riscaldare la casa abbandonata e combattiamo ghiaccio, vento e isolamento solo per superare la stagione.

L'inverno su un'isola fuori dalla rete elettrica significa che niente è facile: tutto gela, le cose si rompono e la sopravvivenza è una routine quotidiana. Più avanti nel video, finalmente usciamo dall'isola e ci dirigiamo verso la terraferma per una pausa tanto necessaria, facendo un giro in motoslitta nell'entroterra di Terranova con gli amici.

Ecco come si presenta la vita su un'isola fuori dalla rete elettrica in inverno: fredda, imprevedibile, ma un'avventura incredibile.

de-DE.title: Ich habe ein verlassenes Haus auf einer abgelegenen Insel gekauft - Den Winter überleben
de-DE.description:
Der Winter hat die Insel erobert und das Leben ohne Stromnetz ist kein Spaß. Ohne Straßen, ohne Strom und durch den Nordatlantik, der uns vom Festland trennt, ist jeder Tag eine neue Herausforderung.

In diesem Video nehmen wir Sie mit in das abgelegene Winterleben hier im Außenhafen von Neufundland. Wir zeigen Ihnen die Herausforderungen, sich warm zu halten, Wasser zu schleppen und Boote bei Minustemperaturen vor dem Einfrieren zu bewahren. Wir sind auf einen alten Steinbrunnen für Trinkwasser angewiesen, schlagen Brennholz, um das verlassene Haus zu heizen, und kämpfen gegen Eis, Wind und Isolation, nur um die Saison zu überstehen.

Im Winter auf einer Insel ohne Stromnetz ist nichts einfach – alles friert ein, Dinge gehen kaputt und das Überleben ist ein täglicher Kampf. Später im Video verlassen wir endlich die Insel und fahren zum Festland für eine dringend benötigte Pause, bei der wir mit Freunden auf dem Schneemobil durch das Hinterland von Neufundland fahren.

So sieht das Leben auf einer Insel ohne Stromnetz im Winter aus – kalt, unvorhersehbar, aber ein Wahnsinnsabenteuer.

id.title: Saya Membeli Rumah Terbengkalai di Pulau Terpencil - Bertahan Hidup di Musim Dingin
id.description:
Musim dingin telah menguasai pulau ini, dan hidup tanpa jaringan listrik di sini bukanlah hal yang mudah. ​​Tanpa jalan raya, tanpa listrik, dan Atlantik Utara yang memisahkan kita dari daratan utama, setiap hari adalah tantangan baru.

Dalam video ini, kami mengajak Anda menyelami kehidupan musim dingin terpencil di Newfoundland. Menunjukkan tantangan untuk tetap hangat, mengangkut air, dan menjaga kapal agar tidak membeku dalam suhu di bawah nol. Kami mengandalkan sumur batu tua untuk air minum, menebang kayu bakar untuk menghangatkan rumah yang ditinggalkan, dan berjuang melawan es, angin, dan isolasi hanya untuk melewati musim ini.

Musim dingin di pulau tanpa jaringan listrik berarti tidak ada yang mudah—semuanya membeku, barang-barang rusak, dan bertahan hidup adalah pekerjaan harian. Kemudian dalam video, kami akhirnya keluar dari pulau dan menuju daratan utama untuk istirahat yang sangat dibutuhkan, mengendarai mobil salju melalui pedalaman Newfoundland bersama teman-teman.

Beginilah kehidupan di pulau tanpa jaringan listrik di musim dingin—dingin, tidak dapat diprediksi, tetapi merupakan petualangan yang luar biasa.

hi.title: मैंने एक सुदूर द्वीप पर एक परित्यक्त घर खरीदा - सर्दी से बचना
hi.description:
सर्दी ने द्वीप पर कब्ज़ा कर लिया है, और यहाँ ऑफ-ग्रिड रहना कोई मज़ाक नहीं है। बिना सड़कों, बिना बिजली और उत्तरी अटलांटिक के हमें मुख्य भूमि से अलग कर देने के कारण, हर दिन एक नई चुनौती है।

इस वीडियो में, हम आपको आउटपोर्ट न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड में सुदूर सर्दियों के जीवन की गहराई में ले जाते हैं। गर्म रहने, पानी ढोने और सबज़ीरो तापमान में नावों को जमने से बचाने की चुनौतियों को दिखाते हैं। हम पीने के पानी के लिए एक पुराने पत्थर के कुएँ पर निर्भर हैं, परित्यक्त घर को गर्म करने के लिए जलाऊ लकड़ी काटते हैं, और बस मौसम को गुज़ारने के लिए बर्फ, हवा और अलगाव से जूझते हैं।

ऑफ-ग्रिड द्वीप पर सर्दी का मतलब है कि कुछ भी आसान नहीं है - सब कुछ जम जाता है, चीज़ें टूट जाती हैं, और जीवित रहना एक रोज़मर्रा की बात है। बाद में वीडियो में, हम आखिरकार द्वीप से उतरते हैं और दोस्तों के साथ न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड के बैककंट्री में स्नोमोबिलिंग करते हुए एक बहुत ज़रूरी ब्रेक के लिए मुख्य भूमि पर जाते हैं।

सर्दियों में ऑफ-ग्रिड द्वीप पर रहना कुछ ऐसा ही दिखता है - ठंडा, अप्रत्याशित, लेकिन एक बेहतरीन रोमांच।

es-US.title: Compré una casa abandonada en una isla remota - Sobreviviendo al invierno
es-US.description:
El invierno se ha apoderado de la isla y vivir sin conexión a la red eléctrica aquí no es ninguna broma. Sin carreteras ni electricidad y con el Atlántico Norte aislándonos del continente, cada día es un nuevo desafío.

En este video, te llevamos a lo más profundo de la vida invernal remota aquí en el puerto exterior de Terranova. Mostramos los desafíos de mantenerse caliente, acarrear agua y evitar que los barcos se congelen en temperaturas bajo cero. Dependemos de un antiguo pozo de piedra para beber agua, cortamos leña para calentar la casa abandonada y luchamos contra el hielo, el viento y el aislamiento solo para pasar la temporada.

El invierno en una isla sin conexión a la red eléctrica significa que nada es fácil: todo se congela, las cosas se rompen y la supervivencia es una tarea diaria. Más adelante en el video, finalmente salimos de la isla y nos dirigimos al continente para un descanso muy necesario, recorriendo en moto de nieve el interior de Terranova con amigos.

Así es la vida en una isla sin conexión a la red eléctrica en invierno: fría, impredecible, pero una gran aventura.

fr-FR.title: J'ai acheté une maison abandonnée sur une île isolée - Survivre à l'hiver
fr-FR.description:
L’hiver a envahi l’île et vivre hors réseau n’est pas une mince affaire. Sans routes, sans électricité et avec l’Atlantique Nord qui nous sépare du continent, chaque jour est un nouveau défi.

Dans cette vidéo, nous vous emmenons au cœur de la vie hivernale isolée ici, dans l’arrière-port de Terre-Neuve. Nous vous montrons les défis de rester au chaud, de transporter de l’eau et d’empêcher les bateaux de geler par des températures négatives. Nous dépendons d’un vieux puits en pierre pour l’eau potable, coupons du bois de chauffage pour chauffer la maison abandonnée et luttons contre la glace, le vent et l’isolement juste pour traverser la saison.

L’hiver sur une île hors réseau signifie que rien n’est facile : tout gèle, les choses se cassent et la survie est un travail quotidien. Plus tard dans la vidéo, nous quittons enfin l’île et nous dirigeons vers le continent pour une pause bien méritée, en parcourant en motoneige l’arrière-pays de Terre-Neuve avec des amis.

Voilà à quoi ressemble la vie insulaire hors réseau en hiver : froide, imprévisible, mais une sacrée aventure.

snippet.title: Full Meeting between President Trump, VP Vance and Ukrainian President Zelensky in Oval Office
snippet.description:
A heated argument broke out between President Donald Trump, Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky, and Vice President JD Vance in the White House Oval Office. The confrontation occurred before a deal was supposed to be made between Ukraine and the United States in which Ukraine would give the U.S. critical minerals in exchange for some unspecified help in dealing with Russia's invasion. Trump and Vance accused Zelensky of being "disrespectful," ungrateful, and of gambling with starting a global war. Before the argument began, President Trump was asked by reporters if he would provide Ukraine with security guarantees, but he declined to affirmatively answer these questions. President Zelensky said Ukraine needed security guarantees and that a ceasefire would not be sufficient. A scheduled news conference between the two leaders was subsequently canceled after this meeting. https://www.c-span.org/event/white-house-event/president-trump-meets-with-ukrainian-president/431338

snippet.description:

Would you rather live through a zombie apocalypse or a robot one? Would you rather have no eyelashes or no finger nails? Would you rather have a watermelon head or a tennis ball head?
These are the great and important questions of our time, and I tackle them here.
But this raises the question, am I alone in my opinions? Or do I agree with everyone else? What does the world think??
This video answers that, and also this video has me in it which is awesome and cool and very interesting.

snippet.title: Marvin Sapp: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
Ashley Pointer | February 28, 2025
The morning that Bishop Marvin Sapp came to NPR, he told me that it was his kids who really emphasized how important it was for him to accept our invitation to perform: "They told me, 'Dad, Tiny Desk is for the culture.' "

Backed by a four-piece band and a six-piece choir, Sapp transforms our office into a sanctuary, performing an 11-song medley of praise and worship hits that span more than three decades in music and ministry. From the moment his set begins, the spirit moves through the room, filling every corner with raw emotion, joy and reverence.

From Sapp's early days with the trailblazing '90s gospel group Commissioned to penning anthems like "Never Would Have Made It" — a song that transcends church walls — his impact is woven into the fabric of Black culture. "What's funny is, I saw some of y'all singing these songs, and y'all weren't even born when I recorded them," Sapp jokes, underscoring his intergenerational influence. Yet, despite his legendary status, Sapp took time after the performance to speak and pray with members of our audience, choosing ministry first, above all else.

SET LIST
"I Believe"
"Not the Time, Not the Place"
"Grace and Mercy"
"Perfect Peace"
"Shout Unto God"
"Here I Am"
"Praise Him in Advance"
"You Are God Alone"
"He Has His Hands on You"
"My Testimony"
"The Best in Me"
"Never Would Have Made It"

MUSICIANS
Bishop Marvin Sapp: vocals
Curtis Lindsey: keys, music director
Thaddeus Johnson: bass
Tavarius "Varo" Johnson: drums
Sam Mitchem: guitar
Christina Michelle: background vocals
Gus Lacy: background vocals
Shaki Wilson: background vocals
Jarmone: background vocals
A. D. Gillispie: background vocals
Melissa Lee: background vocals

TINY DESK TEAM
Producers: Bobby Carter, Ashley Pointer
Director/Editor: Joshua Bryant
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Host/Series Producer: Bobby Carter
Videographers: Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Maia Stern, Mitra I. Arthur
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistant: Dora Levite
Photographer: Michael Zamora
Tiny Desk Copy Editor: Lars Gotrich
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson
VP, Visuals and Music: Keith Jenkins

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the greatest adventure ever built. ⛏️ Tickets are on sale NOW for #MinecraftMovie – only in theaters April 4. https://www.fandango.com/MinecraftMovie

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, “A Minecraft Movie,” directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. 

The film also stars Emma Myers (“Wednesday”), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (“The Color Purple”), Sebastian Hansen (“Just Mercy, “Lisey’s Story”), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival! Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (“Ninety-Five Senses,” “Nacho Libre”) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Ólafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The director’s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (“127 Hours,” “Transformers: Rise of the Beasts”), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (“The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,” “The Meg”), editor James Thomas (“Pokémon: Detective Pikachu”, the “Borat” films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (“The Jungle Book,” “The Batman”), and costume designer Amanda Neale (“The Meg,” “What We Do in the Shadows”). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (“Thor: Ragnarok,” the “LEGO®” movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, “A Minecraft Movie.” The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.title: Get Ready For An Action-Packed Season!
snippet.description:
Buckle up, soldier! The villainous Minion General is striking across the land like a Lightning Spell. There's only one fighting force strong enough to stop him: the Action Heroes!

Clash of Clans "Action Heroes" Season starts March 1st 08:00AM UTC! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

en.title: Get Ready For An Action-Packed Season!
en.description:
Buckle up, soldier! The villainous Minion General is striking across the land like a Lightning Spell. There's only one fighting force strong enough to stop him: the Action Heroes!

Clash of Clans "Action Heroes" Season starts March 1st 08:00AM UTC! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.title: Death of Gene Hackman and His Wife Called 'Suspicious'
snippet.description: A cloud of suspicion surrounds the deaths of Oscar-winning actor Gene Hackman and his wife. The 95-year-old legend and his wife Betsy Arakawa were found dead in their home in Santa Fe, New Mexico. Initial reports said no foul play was suspected and there was speculation they were killed by carbon monoxide poisoning. Now, their deaths are being called, "Suspicious enough in nature to require a thorough search and investigation." Inside Edition's Jim Moret has more.

snippet.title: Apes Freaked Out When I Spoke Their Language
snippet.description:
Thanks to MyHeritage for sponsoring this video – go to https://bit.ly/XIAO_MH and use coupon code XIAO for free shipping on your order!

I spent weeks secretly studying ape communication and then I convinced these apes into thinking I was one of them. Bonobos are the closest living relatives of human beings, and while attempts have been made to teach them to use human language, it is very rare for human beings to try to communicate with bonobos on their terms using bonobo vocalizations and gestures, and so when I attempted to do this as an innocent visitor to this bonobo research center, the bonobos were genuinely shocked and we bonded pretty hard.

I’m running this video as a fundraiser for Ape Initiative, a federally-recognized non-profit which is the world’s only bonobo research center. Bonobos are an endangered species and Ape Initiative works with scientists and educators to help understand bonobo behavior with an aim towards ensuring their preservation in the wild. Consider donating to the fundraiser if you can or visit their website at https://www.apeinitiative.org/

0:00 Introduction
2:17 Where are we?
2:45 What are bonobos?
4:46 Making friends with a bonobo
6:26 Kanzi comes to play
7:45 They were shocked I knew how to do this
8:12 Kanzi uses his human language keyboard
9:23 Bonobos think I'm a bonobo
10:32 Showing my submissiveness
11:48 Scaring me with my back turned
13:01 Closing thoughts

snippet.title: When a Dog Spooks Your Horse! 🐎😱 Helmet Cam POV
snippet.description:
Helmet Cam POV: When a Dog Spooks Your Horse! 🐎😱
Come ride with me in this POV helmet cam 'Get Ready With Me' as I take my horse out for a relaxing ride — until a dog jumps out and spooks my horse! 😱 Watch the unexpected moment unfold as I handle the situation while riding out in the countryside. If you love horse riding, trail rides, and equestrian adventures, this one's for you! 🐴✨"

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Real Madrid 3-1 Man City | Mbappe (3) & Nico Goals
snippet.description:
Manchester City were knocked out this season’s UEFA Champions League after a 6-3 aggregate defeat to Real Madrid.
Pep Guardiola’s side were beaten 3-1 in the second leg at the Santiago Bernabeu with Kylian Mbappe scoring a hat-trick for the current European champions.

After a 3-2 defeat in the first leg at the Etihad, City fell further behind in the tie when the Frenchman scored the opener after just four minutes.

And we suffered a further early early setback with John Stones going off injured after just eight minutes while Erling Haaland was unable to feature in the fixture.

Mbappe scored two more either side of half-time before Nico scored his first goal for City in the dying minutes.

Here you will find all the latest videos from Manchester City, including, all Premier League, Champions League, FA Cup and League Cup goals, highlights, behind-the-scenes footage, training and much more.

Get closer to the likes of Jack Grealish, Bunny Shaw, Kevin De Bruyne, Lauren Hemp, Erling Haaland, Joško Gvardiol, Phil Foden, Vivianne Miedema and the rest of Pep Guardiola & Gareth Taylor's teams!

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Man City 2-3 Real Madrid | Haaland (2), Mbappe, Diaz & Bellingham Goals
snippet.description:
City face a tough task to progress in the Champions League after losing the first play-off leg 3-2 to Real Madrid.

Erling Haaland twice put the Blues ahead in a thrilling encounter, but the Spanish side hit back each time, before snatching victory with almost the final kick of the game.

It leaves City needing to win by at least a goal in the second leg to at least level the aggregate scores and have any chance of progressing after a heart-breaking final seven minutes.

snippet.title: What The Hell Is Shrek 5 Doing??
snippet.description:
I am blindsided by this today. This looks beyond awful! Oh my god... So much for A Minecraft Movie Trailer today, THIS looks to be the new animated punching bag as we now get to see the changed art style of the FIFTH Shrek movie. And it's awful. Also a cast announcement who cares. But is there something more under the surface that's worth praising for this 2026 instalment? Don't get you hopes up. Here's our thoughts. Similar to most peoples, who's first impression of Shrek 5 was likely: What The Hell is Shrek 5 Doing??

snippet.title: Gene Hackman Death Investigation | Santa Fe County Sheriff's Office gives update on latest
snippet.description:
Gene Hackman Found Dead: Oscar-winner Gene Hackman, his wife and one of their dogs were apparently dead for some time before a maintenance worker discovered their bodies at the couple's Santa Fe home, according to investigators.

Hackman, 95, was found dead Wednesday in a mudroom and his 65-year-old wife, Betsy Arakawa, was found in a bathroom next to a space heater, Santa Fe County Sheriff’s Office detectives wrote in a search warrant affidavit. There was an open prescription bottle and pills scattered on a countertop near Arakawa.

Santa Fe County Sheriff's Office gives an update on the death of Gene Hackman. Video from KOAT.

Read more: https://www.abc10.com/article/news/nation-world/actor-gene-hackman-wife-and-their-dog-found-dead-in-their-new-mexico-home/507-f4fbf141-a904-4531-b8e9-daacdc810a24

Bringing Magical Moments to Millennial Farmer Fans:
►https://www.cameo.com/millennialfarmer?utm_campaign=profile_share 

Book The Millennial Farmer to Speak at your Next Event: 
►mnmillennialfarmer@gmail.com 

Zach Johnson, the “Millennial Farmer” is a 5th-generation farmer who’s spent his life growing, working, and learning on his family’s farm. His wit and dry sense of humor appeal to children and adults alike. A product of the millennial generation, his appreciation of new technology blends with his old-fashioned work ethic, and he offers a unique ability to deliver his message in a way that resonates with lifelong farmers as well as those with no knowledge of agriculture. With growing consumer awareness about where their food comes from, Zach has identified the need for an independent voice from the front lines of agriculture. Zach actively promotes agriculture by sharing his day-to-day experiences in the agriculture world while providing farmer-to-farmer education to help facilitate a collaborative conversation between farmers and the public. 
Follow Along 
►https://www.instagram.com/mnmillennialfarmer/ ►https://www.facebook.com/MNMILLENNIALFARMER/ 
►https://twitter.com/farmmillennial 
►https://www.tiktok.com/@millennialfarmer

Edited By: Becky Johnson

snippet.title: WOODY FM x LISA | Most Exclusive Talk Ever In Thailand! เปิดใจเรื่องที่ไม่เคยเล่าที่ไหนมาก่อน
snippet.description:
WOODY FM x LISA | Most Exclusive Talk Ever In Thailand! เปิดใจเรื่องที่ไม่เคยเล่าที่ไหนมาก่อน

Exclusive Talk สุด Deep ครั้งแรกในไทยของลิซ่า! เบื้องหลัง New Chapter ในฐานะศิลปินเดี่ยวอัลบั้ม Alter Ego และการแสดงครั้งแรกในซีรีส์ระดับโลก "The White Lotus" พร้อมเปิดใจเล่าประสบการณ์รับมือกับความคิดเห็นเชิงลบที่ส่งผลต่อจิตใจ และเผชิญหน้า "ซาแซง" ที่ทำให้กลัวที่สุดในชีวิต

#WoodyFM #Woody #วู้ดดี้ #WoodyxLisa #WoodyFMxLisa #LisaxWoody #lisa 

Timestamps 

00:00 Highlight
02:05 1 ปีที่ผ่านมา
02:45 อาหารที่ชอบ
05:38 ช่วงที่เหนื่อยที่สุด
07:17 New Chapter
13:20 รับมือคอมเมนต์เชิงลบ
15:51 ความมั่นใจของลิซ่า
21:21 มีซาแซงเป็นครั้งแรก! 
26:53 The White Lotus

snippet.title: Test Fitting the NEW Engine and it’s a BIG Upgrade! | Franna Crane Project | Part 28
snippet.description:
We’ve been keeping a BIG surprise under wraps… and today’s the big reveal! We’re swapping out the old Perkins engine in our Franna crane for a brand-new Cummins 6BT! In this video, we unbox the new engine, bolt on the bell housing and transmission, and move the rear frame into position. Using the overhead crane, Kurtis carefully lowers the engine into place, but as expected, the existing mounts and saddle are in the way. Since we planned for this, we get all the measurements to design and 3D draw new parts before getting straight to work air arc gouging off the old mounts and saddle to make way for the new setup. While we’re at it, we also remove the rust-damaged plate in the articulation joint. With everything prepped and ground back, the engine bay and rear frame are now ready for the next stage of fabrication!

If you love heavy machinery rebuilds, fabrication, and machining, LIKE, SUBSCRIBE, and turn on NOTIFICATIONS so you don’t miss the next episode!

Watch the full Franna Crane Project series here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUzFN5xVei7UatVhlxlw3576rgwg2RTXf

Join our channel:
We upload new videos every Friday at 5pm AEST! If you want to see more of our videos click LIKE & SUBSCRIBE! You can subscribe to our channel here: https://bit.ly/ceesubscribe

https://www.amazon.com/shop/cuttingedgeengineeringaustralia

Instagram https://instagram.com/cutting_edge_engineering 
Facebook https://www.facebook.com/cuttingedgeengineeringaustralia/ 

About Us:
We're a down-to-earth real life machining and fabrication workshop in Australia. We specialise in helping business in mining and earthmoving to keep their machines running smoothly. We love working on broken parts and the bigger the better! We upload new videos every week showcasing machining, welding, line boring, honing and all the other awesome stuff that goes down in our workshop. Learn how we tackle different projects and see the satisfaction of creating something useful. Subscribe to stay updated on our latest jobs and projects! Follow us on Patreon for even more content and behind-the-scenes glimpses or find us on Tiktok, Facebook and Instagram for a chance to connect with us.

snippet.title: Ruby Franke’s Estranged Husband and Son Break Their Silence on Her Child Abuse Vlogging Scandal
snippet.description:
For the first time, Kevin Franke and his son Chad Franke, 20, are breaking their silence on the shocking child abuse scandal surrounding Ruby Franke and her controversial therapist, Jodi Hildebrandt. Kevin and Chad open up about the dark reality behind their once-popular YouTube channel, 8 Passengers, and how their lives were shattered by manipulation, abuse, and extreme parenting tactics.

At the peak of their fame, the Franke family had 2.5 million subscribers and earned $100,000 per month, but behind the scenes, a disturbing truth was unfolding. Ruby Franke’s extreme discipline methods—promoted by Hildebrandt—led to the eventual arrest and conviction of both women for felony child abuse, resulting in prison sentences of up to 30 years each in 2024.

Kevin Franke, who admits to feelings of guilt and regret, says much of the physical abuse was kept from him—especially during the year Ruby forced him to live apart from the family. He is now estranged from Ruby and filed for divorce in November 2023.

The family is telling their side of the story and reflecting on how they are rebuilding their lives after the horrific abuse that left them deeply traumatized. “I really hope [my mom] becomes a better person and truly tries to change,”says Chad, who currently has no contact with his mother. Watch the new Hulu docuseries, 'Devil in the Family: The Fall of Ruby Franke', streaming February 27, for more on this story.

* If you suspect child abuse, call the Childhelp National Child Abuse Hotline at 1-800-4-A-Child or 1-800-422-4453, or go to www.childhelp.org. All calls are toll-free and confidential. The hotline is available 24/7 in more than 170 languages.

snippet.title: Love Island’s Grace & Luca Tell All in Exclusive Interview
snippet.description:
Fresh from the Love Island: All Stars villa, runners-up Grace and Luca are joining us for their FIRST podcast interview since leaving the show—exclusively on Wednesdays!

Sophie and Melissa get the inside scoop on their time in the villa as they spill all the tea. From Grace setting her sights on Luca from the start to their real thoughts on Ekin-Su and Sammie, no topic is off-limits. Plus, Grace finally sets the record straight on those ‘fake receipts’ drama!

Luca also gets real about the nerves of going back into the villa for a second time as he opens up about the threats to his family. And of course, the burning question—are they official now? Tune in to find out!

#WEDNESDAYS #SOPHIEHABBOO #MELISSATATTAM

snippet.title: MAVERICKS at LAKERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | February 25, 2025
snippet.description:
The Lakers defeated the Mavericks, 107-99 tonight in Los Angeles. LeBron James finished with a team-high 27 points along with 12 rebounds and 3 assists for the Lakers, while Austin Reaves tallied 20 points, 5 assists and 3 rebounds in the game. Kyrie Irving recorded 35 points, 7 rebounds and 5 three pointers. The Lakers improve their record to 35-21 with the win, while the Mavericks fall to 31-28 for the season. The Lakers' next game is Thursday, 2/27/2025, against the Timberwolves on the road (10:30 PM ET, NBA TV), while the Mavericks head home to take on the Hornets on Thursday, 2/27/2025, (8:30 PM ET, KFAA/WFAA/FDSNSE-CHA/TV 64).

snippet.title: Robert De Niro Breaks Down His Most Iconic Characters | GQ
snippet.description:
We didn't have a lot of time with him, but De Niro was kind enough to tell us the stories behind some of his biggest movies. Robert De Niro joins GQ as he revisits some of the most iconic characters from his career so far: from his leading role in _Taxi Driver_ as Travis Bickle, to his portrayal of a young Vito Corleone in _The Godfather Part II._

“Martin Scorsese and Francis Coppola had talked and he wanted me to come out to San Francisco to test with him… I was ready to do that,” De Niro recalls of his casting for _The Godfather Part II._ “Then they called and said ‘it’s okay, you don’t have to come, you have the part’—it was great!” Watch the full episode of GQ’s Iconic Characters as Robert De Niro breaks down his most iconic movie roles.

snippet.title: John Oliver: The 60 Minutes Interview
snippet.description:
John Oliver has been unleashing his searing, satirical take on the U.S., his adopted homeland, for years. The comedian plans to continue for "as long as America has systemic problems."

"60 Minutes" is the most successful television broadcast in history. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 and is still a hit, over 50 seasons later, regularly making Nielsen's Top 10.

snippet.title: HAVOC | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a drug deal gone wrong, a bruised detective must fight his way through a criminal underworld to rescue a politician's estranged son, while unravelling a deep web of corruption and conspiracy that ensnares his entire city.

HAVOC is a high octane action thriller written and directed by Gareth Evans (The Raid, Gangs of London), and starring Tom Hardy, Jessie Mei Li, Justin Cornwell, Quelin Sepulveda, Luis Guzmán, Michelle Waterson, Sunny Pang, Jim Caesar, Xelia Mendes-Jones with Yeo Yann Yann, Timothy Olyphant, and Forest Whitaker.

Coming to Netflix on April 25.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81330790

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

snippet.title: The RTX 50 Disaster
snippet.description:
Sponsor: Thermal Grizzly Duronaut on Amazon - https://geni.us/tpgcPMw
NVIDIA's RTX 50 series GPUs in the Blackwell family now represent the worst GPU launch we have covered in our history of GPU reviews at GN. It was briefly tied with past AMD and NVIDIA launches for the worst, but now, with the missing ROPs in addition to 12VHPWR issues, fake pricing, a paper launch, unannounced loss of PhysX 32-bit support, driver issues in some scenarios, and more, we crown the RTX 5090, 5080, and 5070 Ti launches as being part of the worst we've seen. Congratulations, NVIDIA.

Use our coupon code for 10% off anything on our store while it's active and support us at the same time! Code "ABOUTFKNTIME" at checkout! The best way to support our work is through our store: https://store.gamersnexus.net/

See the impact from missing ROPs in benchmarks: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PEXYZgVfOBM
Watch something actually exciting about the industry - fan testing! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JQtyxRtsqvA
Watch our Fake Prices video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8s4hxa2TjWY
PAPER LAUNCH: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wMd2WHKnceI
Watch our review of the RTX 5070 Ti: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PhtVic3Vm0Y

Like our content? Please consider becoming our Patron to support us: http://www.patreon.com/gamersnexus

TIMESTAMPS

00:00 - The Worst GPU Launch
04:37 - NVIDIA's Response
07:10 - How This Might Have Happened (Speculation)
12:31 - Rant: DISASTROUS LAUNCH
18:36 - Our Theory's Problems: RTX 5080 Isn't Immune
19:51 - Conclusion: AMD's Opportunity

** Please like, comment, and subscribe for more! **

Any advertisements or sponsorships are disclosed within the video ("this video is brought to you by") and above the fold in the description. We do not ever produce paid content or "sponsored content" (meaning that the content is our idea and is not funded externally aside from whatever ad placement is in the beginning) and we do not ever charge manufacturers for coverage.

Follow us in these locations for more gaming and hardware updates:

snippet.title: Starship | Seventh Flight Test
snippet.description:
The first Starship flight test of 2025 flew with ambitious goals: seeking to repeat our previous success of launching and catching the world’s most powerful launch vehicle while putting a redesigned and upgraded Starship through a rigorous set of flight demonstrations.

It served as a reminder that development testing, by definition, can be unpredictable.

On its seventh flight test, Starship successfully lifted off from Starbase in Texas at 4:37 p.m. CT on Thursday, January 16. For the second time ever, the Super Heavy booster returned to the launch site and was caught by the tower. But before Starship could reach space, a fire developed in the aft section leading to a rapid unscheduled disassembly.

As always, success comes from what we learned, and this flight test will help us improve Starship’s reliability as SpaceX seeks to make life multiplanetary.

snippet.title: Chris Harris on Cars: Raw road test of the sensational Ferrari 12 Cilindri
snippet.description: If someone says 'do you fancy a go in a 12 Cilindri?', you say YES! I cannot tell you how much fun these few hours were. Thank you Rafa.

localized.description: If someone says 'do you fancy a go in a 12 Cilindri?', you say YES! I cannot tell you how much fun these few hours were. Thank you Rafa.

es-US.title: Chris Harris en Cars: Prueba en carretera del sensacional Ferrari 12 Cilindri
es-US.description: Si alguien te pregunta "¿te apetece montar en un 12 Cilindi?", ¡dirás que SÍ! No puedo explicarte lo divertidas que fueron estas horas. Gracias, Rafa.

id.title: Chris Harris di Cars: Uji jalan mentah dari Ferrari 12 Cilindri yang sensasional
id.description: Jika seseorang bertanya 'apakah Anda ingin mencoba 12 Cilindi?', Anda akan menjawab YA! Saya tidak dapat menggambarkan betapa menyenangkannya beberapa jam ini. Terima kasih Rafa.

de-DE.title: Chris Harris über Autos: Unverarbeiteter Straßentest des sensationellen Ferrari 12 Cilindri
de-DE.description: Wenn jemand fragt: „Hast du Lust, mal einen 12-Zylinder-Motor auszuprobieren?“, dann sagst du JA! Ich kann dir gar nicht sagen, wie viel Spaß diese paar Stunden gemacht haben. Danke, Rafa.

fr-FR.title: Chris Harris sur les voitures : essai routier brut de la sensationnelle Ferrari 12 Cilindri
fr-FR.description: Si quelqu'un vous dit "ça te dirait de faire un tour dans un 12 Cilindi ?", vous dites OUI ! Je ne peux pas vous dire à quel point ces quelques heures ont été amusantes. Merci Rafa.

hi.title: क्रिस हैरिस की कारों पर राय: सनसनीखेज फेरारी 12 सिलिंड्री का कच्चा रोड टेस्ट
hi.description: अगर कोई आपसे पूछे कि 'क्या आप 12 सिलिंदी में जाना पसंद करेंगे?', तो आप हाँ कहेंगे! मैं आपको बता नहीं सकता कि ये कुछ घंटे कितने मज़ेदार थे। शुक्रिया राफ़ा।

it.title: Chris Harris su Cars: Prova su strada cruda della sensazionale Ferrari 12 Cilindri
it.description: Se qualcuno ti chiede "ti piacerebbe fare un giro su una 12 Cilindi?", tu rispondi SÌ! Non posso dirti quanto sono state divertenti queste poche ore. Grazie Rafa.

ja.title: クリス・ハリスの車評：センセーショナルなフェラーリ12シリンドリの生々しいロードテスト
ja.description: 誰かが「12 Cilindi に乗ってみませんか?」と言ったら、YES と答えてください。この数時間がどれほど楽しかったか、言葉では言い表せません。ありがとう、ラファ。

pt-BR.title: Chris Harris sobre carros: Teste de estrada bruto do sensacional Ferrari 12 Cilindri
pt-BR.description: Se alguém disser "você gostaria de ir em um 12 Cilindi?", você diz SIM! Não consigo dizer o quanto essas poucas horas foram divertidas. Obrigado, Rafa.

snippet.title: Dave Chappelle Delivers Unforgettable Speech & Stands Strong for the People | NAACP Image Awards '25
snippet.description:
Dave Chappelle is recognized as one of the greatest comedians of all time. He is the 2019 recipient of the prestigious Mark Twain Prize for American Humor. Chappelle’s work has earned him more than 30 nominations and awards in television and film for projects that include his groundbreaking sketch comedy television series Chappelle’s Show, comedy specials, and guest appearances on Saturday Night Live. Chappelle has received five Emmy awards, including three for his Netflix comedy specials Sticks & Stones (2020) and Equanimity & The Bird Revelation (2018), and two for hosting Saturday Night Live (2017 and 2021). Chappelle has won six GRAMMY® Awards for Best Comedy Album, winning most recently in 2025 with The Dreamer.

snippet.title: Damon & Marlon Wayans Share Loving, Hilarious Speech at NAACP Image Awards '25 Hall of Fame
snippet.description:
The Wayans family has redefined comedy and entertainment for decades. Led by Keenen Ivory Wayans, creator of In Living Color, they broke barriers in film, TV, and stand-up comedy, launching the careers of stars like Jim Carrey, Jamie Foxx, and Jennifer Lopez. With a fearless approach to storytelling, Keenen and his siblings—Damon, Marlon, Shawn, and Kim—have created iconic works like Scary Movie, White Chicks, and The Wayans Bros. The next generation, including Damon Wayans Jr., is continuing the legacy, with Marlon starring in Respect and Air, and the family gearing up for a Scary Movie reboot in 2026.
